Free JAR data quality checking

Contingency table creation

tab_conting <- data.frame(matrix(nrow = 3, ncol = 3))
rownames(tab_conting) <- levels(data_FreeJAR$Hedonic_category)
colnames(tab_conting) <- c("Too much","Not enough","JAR")

tab_conting[,1] <- aggregate(data_FreeJAR$Too_much, by=list(Category=data_FreeJAR$Hedonic_category), FUN=sum)[,2]
tab_conting[,2] <- aggregate(data_FreeJAR$Not_enough, by=list(Category=data_FreeJAR$Hedonic_category), FUN=sum)[,2]
tab_conting[,3] <- aggregate(data_FreeJAR$JAR, by=list(Category=data_FreeJAR$Hedonic_category), FUN=sum)[,2]

Contingency table representation

tab_conting_plot <- tab_conting
tab_conting_plot$hedonic_categ <- rownames(tab_conting)
new_tab_conting <- gather(tab_conting_plot, key=Terms, value = Value, -4)

p_value_desc <- rep("non significant",9)
x <- descfreq(tab_conting)
for (i in 1:3){
  for (j in 1:9){
    if (names(x[i])==new_tab_conting[j,1]){
      for(m in 1:length(rownames(x[[i]]))){
        if (gsub("[.]"," ",rownames(x[[i]])[m])==new_tab_conting[j,2]){
          p_value_desc[j] <- x[[i]][m,5]
        }
      }
    }
  }
}

p_value_01 <- p_value_desc

for (i in 1:9){
  if (p_value_desc[i]!="non significant"){
    p_value_01[i] <- "significant"
  }
}

new_tab_conting$pvalue <- p_value_01

ggplot(new_tab_conting, aes(x=hedonic_categ, y=Value, fill=Terms, alpha=pvalue))+
  geom_bar(width = 0.4, position = position_dodge(0.6), stat = "identity")+
  scale_fill_manual(values=c("#3CAEA3","darkorange1","red"))+
  coord_flip()+
  xlab("")+
  scale_y_continuous(breaks = seq(0,60,10), limits = c(0,60))+
  ylab("")+
  theme(
    panel.background = element_rect(fill = "white", colour = NA),
    panel.grid.major.x = element_line(colour = "grey"),
    legend.position = "bottom",
    legend.title = element_blank(),
    legend.text = element_text(size=13),
    axis.text.y = element_text(size = 13, face = "bold")
    
  )

MFA

First table

pdt <- levels(data_FreeJAR$Product)
hedocat <- data.frame(matrix(data="NA",nrow=8, ncol=30))
colnames(hedocat) <- unique(data_FreeJAR$Number)
rownames(hedocat) <- pdt
nb <- seq(from=1, to=240, by=8)
a=1
for (i in nb){
  data_pdt <- data_FreeJAR[i:(i+7),c(5,6)]
  data_pdt <- data_pdt[order(data_pdt[,1], decreasing = F),]
  hedocat [,a]<- data_pdt[,2]
  a=a+1
}

Sentiment Mapping

Import the data

data_FreeJAR <- read.csv2("data_cheese_30_ANG.csv")
pola_dic <- read.csv2("polarity_dictionary.csv")

Clean the data

Unaccent <- function(text) {
  text <- gsub("[`^~\"]", " ", text)
  text= gsub("[]", "e", text)
  text= gsub("[]", "o", text)
  text= gsub("[]", "i", text)
  text= gsub("[]", "a", text)
  text= gsub("[]", "u", text)
  text= gsub("[`^~.'!?;\"]", " ", text)
  return(text)
}

data_FreeJAR$FreeJAR_description <- tolower(data_FreeJAR$FreeJAR_description)
data_FreeJAR$FreeJAR_description <- Unaccent(data_FreeJAR$FreeJAR_description)
pola_dic$Word <- tolower(pola_dic$Word)
pola_dic$Word <- Unaccent(pola_dic$Word)

data_FreeJAR$FreeJAR_description <- gsub("stick to the palate", "stick'to'the'palate", data_FreeJAR$FreeJAR_description)
data_FreeJAR$FreeJAR_description <- gsub("sticks to the palate", "sticks'to'the'palate", data_FreeJAR$FreeJAR_description)
data_FreeJAR$FreeJAR_description <- gsub("just right", "just'right", data_FreeJAR$FreeJAR_description)
data_FreeJAR$FreeJAR_description <- gsub("don t", "dont", data_FreeJAR$FreeJAR_description)
data_FreeJAR$FreeJAR_description <- gsub("doesn t", "doesnt", data_FreeJAR$FreeJAR_description)
data_FreeJAR$FreeJAR_description <- gsub("just the right", "just'the'right", data_FreeJAR$FreeJAR_description)
data_FreeJAR$FreeJAR_description <- gsub("easy to eat", "easy'to'eat", data_FreeJAR$FreeJAR_description)
data_FreeJAR$FreeJAR_description <- gsub("full bodied", "full'bodied", data_FreeJAR$FreeJAR_description)
data_FreeJAR$FreeJAR_description <- gsub("st nectaire", "st'nectaire", data_FreeJAR$FreeJAR_description)

data_FreeJAR$FreeJAR_description <- gsub("too ", "too'", data_FreeJAR$FreeJAR_description)
pola_dic$Word <- gsub("_", "'", pola_dic$Word)

Highlighting drivers of liking and disliking

Unaccent_2 <- function(text) {
  text <- gsub("[`^~\"]", " ", text)
  text= gsub("[]", "e", text)
  text= gsub("[]", "o", text)
  text= gsub("[]", "i", text)
  text= gsub("[]", "a", text)
  text= gsub("[]", "u", text)
  text= gsub("[`^~'!?;\"]", " ", text)
  return(text)
}

data_FreeJAR$FreeJAR_description <- tolower(data_FreeJAR$FreeJAR_description)
data_FreeJAR$FreeJAR_description <- Unaccent_2(data_FreeJAR$FreeJAR_description)

Unstop <- function(text) {
  text= gsub("[`^~'.!?;\"]", " ", text)
  return(text)
}
